text: The St. Louis Lambert International Airport is an airport. It is the main airport in St. Louis, Missouri area. It is 14 miles north of St. Louis. It is the largest and busiest airport in Missouri, with over 259 daily departures. ==References== Category:20th-century establishments in Missouri Category:1923 establishments in the United States Category:Airports in the United States Category:Buildings and structures in Missouri Category:Transport in Missouri Category:St. Louis, Missouri
